<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">اللَّاحِجَةُ الْأُخْرَى:</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>الصَّخْرَةُ الْقَائِمَةُ بَيْنَ اللَّاحِجَةِ وَالْفَدَفْدَةِ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>⦗١٩٧⦘<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">قَالَتْ سَرِيَّةُ بِنْتُ شَبِيبٍ الْجُمَحِيَّةُ وَكَانَتْ نَازِلَةً بِذَاتِ الرِّمَاضِ وَجَارَتُهَا فَاطِمَةُ بِنْتُ الْمُغِيرَةِ بْنِ الْعَاصِ نَازِلَةً عَلَى اللَّاحِجَةِ فَقَالَتْ:</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c4">[البحر المتقارب]</span><a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>سَرِيَّةُ سَبَيْتِ اللَّوَاحِجَ مِنْ مَنْزِلٍ ... وَلَا مِثْلَ جَارِكِ يَا فَاطِمَهْ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>بِدَفْعِ صِيغٍ فُوَيْقَ الْمُرَارِ ... فَالدَّوْحُ فَالصَّخْرَةُ الْقَائِمَهْ<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ:</span> فَأَجَابَتْهَا فَاطِمَةُ:<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c4">[البحر المتقارب]</span><a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>إِذَا جِئْتَ حَيًّا بِذَاتِ الرِّمَاضِ ... فَأَبْلِغْ سَرِيَّةَ عَنْ فَاطِمَهْ<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>وَقُولَا فَقَدْ جَاءَنِي قَوْلُهَا ... أَيَقْظَى تَحَدَّثْتِ أَمْ نَائِمِهْ؟<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>ذَمَمْتِ اللَّوَاحِجَ فَاسْتَغْفِرِي ... وَتُوبِي إِلَى اللهِ يَا ظَالِمَهْ<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>فَلَوْ بِتِّ فِي مَنْزِلِي لَيْلَةً ... تَمَنَّيْتُ أَنَّكِ لِي خَادِمِهْ<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>بِأَبْطُحَ حُلْوَاجِ دَمْثِ الرُّبَا ... بِمَا شِئْتِ مِنْ دَوْحَةٍ نَاعِمَهْ<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>